  "prompt": "What's your definition of \"friends\"?",
  "response": "Friendship is a close and trusting relationship between two or more people. Friends typically share mutual affection, support, and understanding. They enjoy spending time together, whether engaging in activities, having conversations, or simply being in each other's company. Friendships are characterized by loyalty, empathy, and a willingness to help each other. True friends are there for each other during both good and challenging times, offering emotional support and encouragement.",
